function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
	
	id_Self = Hydra.QuestGetOwner()

	actorClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(ID_ROZA)
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(actorClone) then
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(actorClone, ID_ROZA_CRY, "NPC_WALK", true)
		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(actorClone, ID_ROZA_CRY)
		Hydra.QActorSetAnimSetOverride(actorClone, ANIM_CRY)
		Hydra.QActorWait(actorClone, 1.5)
		Hydra.QActorPlayConversation(CONVO_ROZA_02, id_Self, actorClone)
		Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(actorClone, CONVO_ROZA_02)
		Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(actorClone, 1)
	end
	
end

function Start(idActorPlayer, idItem)
id_Self = Hydra.QuestGetOwner()
Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(CONVO_PC, id_Self)
end
